  "steps": [
    "Grow cells till confluent - cells like to grow in clumps Media used - RPMI + 10% FBS + b-mercaptoethanol Ref: http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17334670",
    "Plate 50,000 c/ well in a 24 well plate in 500 ul Add 10-50ng/ml of PMA for 72 hours",
    "After 3 days - rest cells for 16hours",
    "Gamma stimulate with 10-50U IFNg o/n - use for PAMP stimulation"
